  <brief_title>Effect of Peripheral Electrical Stimulation (PES) on Brain Response to Glucose Stimuli</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Short Peripheral Electrical Stimulation (PES) on Brain Response to Glucose Stimuli Evaluated by BOLD and Functional Diffusion MRI: a Crossover Pilot Study</official_title>
